Catherine Nakalembe bụ onye ọkà mmụta sayensị na-ahụ maka ihe dịpụrụ adịpụ na ọbọdọ Uganda na onye na-eme nchọpụta na Mahadum Maryland (UMD) na Ngalaba Sayensị Geographical na NASA Harvest Africa program Director. Nnyocha ya gụnyere ụkọ mmiri ozuzo, ọrụ ugbo na nchekwa nri.
N'afọ 2020, e nyere Nakalembe onyinye nri Afrika.
Ọ natara onyinye Group on Earth Observations nke mbụ onyinyé nke onye kacha mma na afo 2019.
Ọ bụ onye nrite nke ihe onyinyé 2020 UMD Research Excellence Honoree. N'afọ 2022, ọ natara ihe nrite  jubilii ọla edo nke Ugandan (onye nkịtị)
Onye isi ala Yoweri Museveni nyere ya nne na nna ya.

Nakalembe lụrụ Sebastian Deffner, onye osote prọfesọ nke Physics na Mahadum Maryland, Baltimore County (UMBC).
Ha nwere ụmụ abụọ.
